<section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-6 md:px-20" style="background: #F5F2EC;">
  <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-36 md:text-44 font-medium mb-2" style="color: #1C2E23;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="font-mono-spec text-12 mb-10" style="color: #8A9490;">Last updated: March 5, 2026</p>

    <div class="font-heading text-15 font-light space-y-8" style="color: #4A5550; line-height: 1.8;">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-20 font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #1C2E23;">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect only the information you voluntarily provide:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>First name</strong> — so we can address you personally</li>
          <li><strong>Email address</strong> — so we can send you the research report and product updates</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We do not collect payment information, phone numbers, physical addresses, or any other personal data through our waitlist or quiz forms.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-20 font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #1C2E23;">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Deliver your free research report ("The Ancestral Microbiome Report")</li>
          <li>Send you product launch updates and educational content</li>
          <li>Improve our website and marketing based on aggregate analytics</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We will never sell your information to third parties.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-20 font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #1C2E23;">3. Data Storage & Processing</h2>
        <p>Your data is stored securely using:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — hosted on AWS infrastructure in the United States</li>
          <li><strong>Klaviyo</strong> — SOC 2 Type II compliant email platform</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">Both services maintain industry-standard security practices including encryption at rest and in transit.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-20 font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #1C2E23;">4. Tracking & Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Meta Pixel</strong> — to measure advertising effectiveness</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> — to understand website usage</li>
          <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — to load typography (may set cookies)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">You can opt out of tracking by using browser extensions like uBlock Origin or by adjusting your browser's cookie settings.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-20 font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #1C2E23;">5. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. Your data is shared only with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — database hosting</li>
          <li><strong>Klaviyo</strong> — email delivery</li>
          <li><strong>Meta</strong> — advertising measurement (anonymized)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-20 font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #1C2E23;">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Unsubscribe</strong> from emails at any time (link in every email)</li>
          <li><strong>Request a copy</strong> of the data we hold about you</li>
          <li><strong>Request deletion</strong> of your data from our systems</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:hello@basecodehealth.com" class="underline" style="color: #C4783A;">hello@basecodehealth.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-20 font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #1C2E23;">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>If we make material changes to this policy, we will notify you via email. Continued use of our website after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-20 font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #1C2E23;">8. Contact</h2>
        <p>BaseCode Inc.<br>Toronto, Canada<br>
          <a href="mailto:hello@basecodehealth.com" class="underline" style="color: #C4783A;">hello@basecodehealth.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

